      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve definitely found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
