    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest standards and presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear or creasing, while the original floor mats look untouched. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. Garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection. It drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it first rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
